pageProduct.name: Vita Bubs Kids Digestive Health Goat Milk + Probiotics 60 Chewable Tablets
pageProduct.description:

General Information

Vita Bubs Goat Milk + Probiotics is a premium multi-strain formulation with 5 billion probiotics per chew. Supports a healthy digestive system, promotes the growth of good gut bacteria and supports the immune system to fight illness. Contains Easy to Digest Australian Goat Milk. With natural apple flavour for a great tasting children's formulation!


Vita Bubs is brought to you by Bubs, trusted by Australian families and dedicated to children's nutrition. The Vita Bubs range is based on scientific evidence and is proudly Australian Owned and Made.

Suitable For: 2 - 12 years

Size: 60 chewables

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each chewable tablet contains:
Total Probiotics 5.0 billion CFU
Lactobacillus plantarum 4.25 Billion CFU
Lactobacillus rhamnosus 0.75 Billion CFU
Goat Milk 200mg

Contains: Contains Lactose, Gluten, Sucralose, Soya beans, Sulphites and Sugars from Fructooligosacchrise.

Allergen Contains: Gluten| Lactose| Soybean| Sulphites

Directions

Chew, do not swallow whole.
Children 2 - 12 years: take 1 tablet a day under supervision or as professionally prescribed.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25C in a dry place away from direct sunlight. Do not sure if seal under lid is broken or missing. Use within 60 day after opening.
